---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Sarakpy NY">
  <section style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 0.9fr; gap: 2rem; align-items: center;">
    <div>
      <p class="muted">Data Science, Statistics, and Machine Learning Student at ENSAE Paris</p>
      <h1>
        Student in Data Science, Statistics, and Machine Learning, interested in
        Scientific Machine Learning, AI, and Deep Learning
      </h1>
      <p>
        I am a student in data science, statistics, and machine learning at ENSAE Paris,
        with experience in both applied and research-oriented machine learning projects.
      </p>
      <p>
        My interests include scientific machine learning, AI, and deep learning, and I am
        building toward PhD opportunities while developing strong technical and analytical foundations.
      </p>

      <div class="button-group">
        <a class="button primary" href="/projects">View Projects</a>
        <a class="button" href="/cv">View CV</a>
        <a class="button" href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <img
        src="/images/ny-profile.jpg"
        alt="Portrait of Sarakpy NY"
        style="width: 100%; max-width: 320px; border-radius: 18px; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; margin: 0 auto;"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Research Interests</h2>
    <p>
      Scientific machine learning, deep learning, statistical learning,
      trustworthy AI, sequence modeling, representation learning, and applied
      machine learning for real-world systems.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Selected Projects</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Manifesto ML System Deployment</h3>
      <p>
        Built and deployed a reproducible machine learning system with modular training pipelines,
        experiment tracking, API serving, containerization, CI/CD, and Kubernetes deployment.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Fairness via Representation Neutralization</h3>
      <p>
        Studied fairness-aware classification on the COMPAS dataset and analyzed the trade-off
        between predictive performance and fairness metrics.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Party Influence in French Electoral Manifestos</h3>
      <p>
        Analyzed French electoral manifestos using NLP, topic modeling, and regression to study
        the drivers of political discourse.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>